OL,3,CKneecap rapper: 'We are not
OL,4,Cantisemitic'
OL,6,FKneecap rapper Liam Og O hAnnaidh has
OL,7,Fsaid that labelling the group as
OL,8,Fantisemitic means people "water that
OL,9,Fterm down".
OL,11,FThe group were interviewed by the Big
OL,12,FIssue after it was ruled the rapper,
OL,13,Fwho performs under the stage name Mo
OL,14,FChara, will not face a terror trial
OL,15,Fafter being accused of displaying a
OL,16,Fflag in support of proscribed terror
OL,17,Forganisation Hezbollah at a gig.
OL,26,@pD@ZOUqD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
