FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773885784
OL,3,CKneecap rapper: 'We are not
OL,4,Cantisemitic'
OL,6,FO hAnnaidh told the magazine: "When
OL,7,Fyou start labelling bands and people
OL,8,Fwho speak out against Israel as
OL,9,Fantisemitic, what you do is water that
OL,10,Fterm down.
OL,12,F"We are not antisemitic."
OL,14,FO hAnnaidh also said it was
OL,15,F"impossible" to remember everything
OL,16,Fthat happens during a performance.
OL,26,@nD@_OUtD@AOUtD@YO]wD@AOUwD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773885784
OL,3,CKneecap rapper: 'We are not
OL,4,Cantisemitic'
OL,6,F"When you're playing a gig it's
OL,7,Fimpossible to be perfectly conscious
OL,8,Fall the time. I don't remember all `
OL,9,Fand that's not just from drink, that's
OL,10,Fpure adrenaline," he told the Big
OL,11,FIssue.
OL,13,FBand member Moglai Bap said the group
OL,14,Fis "from the north of Ireland".
OL,16,F"We know about f****** religious
OL,17,Fconflicts, people using religion as a
OL,18,Fway to murder, maim and all this
OL,19,Fstuff," he added.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@QO]vD@DOUvD@^O]xD@AOU{D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
