OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773885784
OL,3,CKneecap rapper: 'We are not
OL,4,Cantisemitic'
OL,6,F"We are against any discrimination in
OL,7,Fany form."
OL,9,FThe alleged offence was said to have
OL,10,Ftaken place at a gig at the O2 Forum
OL,11,Fin Kentish Town, north London, on
OL,12,FNovember 21 2024.
OL,14,FBut the case was thrown out in
OL,15,FSeptember last year, with chief
OL,16,Fmagistrate Paul Goldspring ruling the
OL,17,Fproceedings were "instituted
OL,18,Funlawfully".
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@JO]yD@ROUzD@KO]
