PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773885784
OL,3,CKneecap rapper: 'We are not
OL,4,Cantisemitic'
OL,6,FThe Crown Prosecution Service (CPS)
OL,7,Fappealed against the decision at the
OL,8,FHigh Court at a hearing in January,
OL,9,Fwith the rapper opposing the challenge.
OL,11,FIn a judgment last week, two judges at
OL,12,Fthe High Court upheld the decision and
OL,13,Fdismissed the CPS appeal.
OL,15,FThe full interview can be read in
OL,16,FMonday's Big Issue, on sale from
OL,17,Fstreet vendors and online via
OL,18,Fbigissue.com.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
